TopicTitle: Stock Delorean Craft File and Youtube Video

Articles.Content:
Just thought I'd post a download link to a stock Delorean I made for a cheesy youtube video.

No Hobos/Kerbals were harmed in the making of this pile of ****... mostly.

Download Link: https://www.dropbox.com/sh/kbvfuygpnany5xb/AACxPhi_ZbHrIID669XEoK8oa?dl=0

Press "1" to turn on internal combustion engine

Press "F9" to go backward in time

Press "." to go forward in time

Set infinite fuel and press "Z" for flame trail

Spam space bar to see what space bar does

Edit in space plane hangar to add more boosters

Comes with:

1x Four stroke "Burrito Bob" engine

56 capacity Burrito fuel tank

1x "Get the Flux outa here" Capacitor

4x Self deflating tires (Perfect for packing away and storing)

1x Advanced friction-less braking system

1x Stayputnik anti-anti-gravity device

Warning, Brakes, Flat Tires, and Hobos not covered under warranty
